Broken Hill Proprietary Co Ltdsaid it will integrate Utah International Inc, which it boughtthree years ago, under a common management structure.    The company said effective June 1, when Utah InternationalChairman Alexander Wilson retires, James Curry will becomechairman and chief executive officer and a new BHP-UtahMinerals International board will be named. Curry is currentlyexecutive vice president of Utah International.    BHP Petroleum (Americas) Inc, formerly part of UtahInternational, will become a subsidiary of BHP's renamed BHPPetroleum International, headquartered in Melbourne. Reuter&#3;